439
00:30:41,384 --> 00:30:42,454
<i>Detektif?</i>

440
00:30:45,753 --> 00:30:48,194
<i>Kau mau menikahi putriku?</i>

441
00:30:48,854 --> 00:30:50,394
<i>Kau itu ambisius...</i>

442
00:30:50,394 --> 00:30:52,063
