00:30:54,334 --> 00:30:55,963
<i>Ini simpanan yang saya miliki untuk pernikahan.</i>

444
00:30:56,463 --> 00:30:57,503
<i>Silakan diperiksa.</i>

445
00:31:01,973 --> 00:31:03,543
<i>Kandidat partai lawan, Park Soo Yong.</i>

